data.description: Welcome to the Pinnacle Club! Step into this stunning M/I home featuring an open floor plan with numerous updates. The kitchen boasts 42'' cabinets, soft-close drawers, pantry, breakfast bar, and SS appliances, including a gas stove with griddle. The owner's suite offers a cathedral ceiling, spacious walk-in closet, and a master bath with double sinks and a standing shower. Entertain in style in the all-vinyl fenced backyard and patio. Enjoy ceramic tile in both bathrooms and the laundry area, cozy carpet in the bedrooms, and sleek hardwood plank flooring throughout the rest of the house.  HOA includes access to community center with pool, fitness center, game room, parks, tennis courts, basketball court, and paved trails.
